atory to appeal to human men.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":2},{"s":["^It makes them feel bad about the world when they get stuck working in the Lamplighter's Guild, thus incentivizing violence against the system.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.2.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-2","flg":2},{"s":["^Nationalism promotes terrible, hateful ideas. We don't want to be feudal states of old. Nor do we want a repeat of the Arcane Era madness. We want a liberal, modern man. One who is nice, and calm, and loving, and never hurts anybody ever.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Why should <i>you</i> not be allowed to dream in the modern world? ","#","^str","/#","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-0.12.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Because I am dangerous. Only women and non-humans should be allowed to exist in the future.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-0.12.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":2},{"s":["^I'm allowed to dream. But only in bite-sized, moderate ways, as to not scare the less fortunate.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-0.12.2.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-2","flg":2},{"s":["^We had our chance, and we made the Coast War happen. Now it's time for someone else to take the reins.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-0.12.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-0.12.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-2":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-0.12.c-2.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.2.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Violence is not always the answer- but if there is no <i>capability of violence</i>, then what stops the system from walking all over you? ","#","^str","/#","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-1.12.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^The social contract?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-1.12.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":2},{"s":["^Democracy?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-1.12.2.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-2","flg":2},{"s":["^They would never...",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-1.12.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^That has already been broken. ","#","^str","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-1.12.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^If democracy is your saving grace, what's stopping the system from removing that as well? ","#","^str","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-2":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-1.12.c-2.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.2.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^They would. They <i>are</i>. ","#","^str","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-2":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-2.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.2.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^There is nothing admirable about a man incapable of force. ","#","^str","/#","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-2.12.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^In an ideal modern city-life, you wouldn't need force.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.c-2.12.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":["^It is in such a utopia that manly force would especially need to be honed. ","#","^str","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"g-0":["^There is a self-destructive hatred festering within men. Within you. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^Some might say it is driven by the forces of various powers in the world. Some might say it is inherent to this Post-War Era. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^But it does not help anyone. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^A man is not inherently evil for desiring greatness. Nor is he mad for throwing himself into danger. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^There is always a need for men to <i>take and rule and protect</i>. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^What is needed, is a way for men to dream freely, to aim towards the ultimate greatness of the self - aimed at helping everyone around. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^So they do not become <i>thieves or tyrants or ruthless gatekeepers</i>. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^If there are no positive outlets for these desires, then that is exactly where they will end up. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^A generation of men told to be calm and nice will grow up to be violent and wild. A generation of men told to be <b>COMPETENT</b> and <b>GOOD</b> will grow up to be wise kings and lovable people. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^Simple as. ","#","^str","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.g-0.50.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-3","flg":2},{"s":["^I see.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.g-0.51.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-4","flg":2},{"s":["^I simply don't agree.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.g-0.52.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-5","flg":2},{"s":["^I see the point. But I think it's more complex than that.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.g-0.53.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-6","flg":2},{"s":["^That sounds about right.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-3":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.g-0.c-3.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.50.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^You do. ","#","^str","/#","\n",{"->":"Q_Witness.0.g-4"},{"#f":5}],"c-4":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.g-0.c-4.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.51.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Then you need to spend more time understanding yourself. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^Or you will continue down this false road of femininity. ","#","^str","/#","\n",{"->":"Q_Witness.0.g-4"},{"#f":5}],"c-5":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.g-0.c-5.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.52.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^It always is. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^Annoyingly so. ","#","^str","/#","\n",{"->":"Q_Witness.0.g-4"},{"#f":5}],"c-6":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-10.12.g-0.c-6.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.53.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Of course it does. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^You're the one who thinks it. Every day. Every night. ","#","^str","/#","\n",{"->":"Q_Witness.0.g-4"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-11":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-3.finally.c-11.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.2.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-4"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5,"#n":"finally"}],{"#f":5}],"g-4":["^Feels like you might be leaning in the wrong direction here. ","#","^dex","/#","\n","^The goal isn't to break yourself for some illusionary audience. ","#","^dex","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-4.10.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-12","flg":2},{"s":["^It's not?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-4.11.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-13","flg":2},{"s":["^That's true, it's-",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-12":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-4.c-12.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.10.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-5"},{"#f":5}],"c-13":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-4.c-13.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.11.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-5"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-5":["^Oh yes. ","#","^dex","/#","\n","^<i>Risk assessment</i>, baby! ","#","^dex","/#","\n","^The larger that creature is, the more you should be getting paid. ","#","^dex","/#","\n","^Not in troves or loot- that shit's a nice bonus, but you gotta get this on paper before you dive in. ","#","^dex","/#","\n","^If you're ever fighting a troll again, you'll be doing so for a maximized hourly rate with every possible gruesome death calculated into that final price. ","#","^dex","/#","\n","^Your life on the line? That pouch is getting fat. Them's the rules. ","#","^dex","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-5.30.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-14","flg":2},{"s":["^Like... the Pest Control Guild?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-5.31.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-15","flg":2},{"s":["^I've heard about clerics who go into freelancing. Could be cool.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-5.32.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-16","flg":2},{"s":["^I'm not for sale.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-14":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-5.c-14.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.30.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Sure. But like, way more lucrative. ","#","^dex","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-6"},{"#f":5}],"c-15":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-5.c-15.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.31.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Could be REAL cool. ","#","^dex","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-6"},{"#f":5}],"c-16":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-5.c-16.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.32.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Can you even say that with a straight face? ","#","^dex","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-6"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-6":["^Clerics are in high demand, especially these days. Clerics with your kind of esoteric know-how? ","#","^dex","/#","\n","^<i>Invaluable</i>. ","#","^dex","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-6.10.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-17","flg":2},{"s":["^Right. I'm not sure this is for me.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-6.11.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-18","flg":2},{"s":["^I do like getting paid a livable wage.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-17":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-6.c-17.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.10.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^You know for damn sure that you're just gonna keep throwing yourself into danger like this. So GET PAID for it, dumbass! ","#","^dex","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-7"},{"#f":5}],"c-18":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-6.c-18.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.11.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^OH yes. The Towers are infamous for their tight budgets after all. ","#","^dex","/#","\n","^Gotta make a living somehow. ","#","^dex","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-7"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-7":["^Taking the gamble for pay is good, sure. ","#","^cha","/#","\n","^But to actually live to tell the tale? For that, you need more than luck. ","#","^cha","/#","\n","^You need the <b>Luck of the Fool</b>. ","#","^cha","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-7.15.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-19","flg":2},{"s":["^What? I'm not stupid.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-7.16.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-20","flg":2},{"s":["^I'm lucky?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-7.17.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-21","flg":2},{"s":["^Yes please.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-19":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-7.c-19.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.15.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Stupid is in the eye of the beholder. ","#","^cha","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-8"},{"#f":5}],"c-20":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-7.c-20.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.16.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Well... ","#","^cha","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-8"},{"#f":5}],"c-21":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-7.c-21.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.17.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-8"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-8":["^Every time you head down here it's a gamble. Every time you take on a job - and there will surely be even more ruthless jobs than that troll in the future - you will roll the die. ","#","^cha","/#","\n","^That die being a fifty-fifty chance of death and destruction. What did the red one call it? ","#","^cha","/#","\n","^Getting <i>bloodmisted</i>? ","#","^cha","/#","\n","^Instantaneous smashing. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^That's it. That's what you're risking every time. ","#","^cha","/#","\n","^So embrace it. Focus on being really, really lucky. ","#","^cha","/#","\n","^You have survived long enough on gut and feeling and ultimately pointless gambles. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^It is time to calculate your odds. Properly. ","#","^int","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-8.40.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-22","flg":2},{"s":["^Calcu-late? What's that?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-8.41.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-23","flg":2},{"s":["^Tell me more.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-22":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-8.c-22.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.40.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-9"},{"#f":5}],"c-23":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-8.c-23.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.41.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-9"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-9":["^As you can clearly evaluate, each time you take on a challenge, your outcomes are quite extreme. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^It appears you are just as likely to succeed in an unlikely and extreme manner, as much as you commonly find yourself in a radical and rather terrible failure. ","#","^int","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-9.10.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-24","flg":2},{"s":["^That might be true.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-9.11.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-25","flg":2},{"s":["^I don't agree with that assessment.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-24":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-9.c-24.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.10.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^It is. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-10"},{"#f":5}],"c-25":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-9.c-25.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.11.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Then you are wrong. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-10"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-10":["^Even by recognizing your personal skill level involved in any particular task, the overwhelming power of CHANCE is evidently your clearest ally. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^This is bad. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^Instead, let us lean upon the Strings for balance. A tightly strung balance, one borne out of a beautifully <b>Curved, Yet Balanced Bell</b>. ","#","^int","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-10.15.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-26","flg":2},{"s":["^What?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-10.16.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-27","flg":2},{"s":["^A... bell-curve?",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-26":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-10.c-26.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.15.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-11"},{"#f":5}],"c-27":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-10.c-27.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.16.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Yes. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-11"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-11":["^If you before had an equal chance of each outcome, which is quite volatile, this would instead allow you to take control of the outcome, aligning each attempt around the center- the <i>average</i>. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^This would reliably increase your odds at succeeding at tasks you are equipped to handle, while dramatically decreasing your failure rate at those you are not. ","#","^int","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-11.10.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-28","flg":2},{"s":["^I'm not entirely sure what this means.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-11.11.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-29","flg":2},{"s":["^I understand what this means.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-28":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-11.c-28.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.10.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^In short: the bell curve allows you to rely more on your own abilities, rather than random chance. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-12"},{"#f":5}],"c-29":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-11.c-29.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.11.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Obviously. It is quite rudimentary. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-12"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-12":["^Of course, this would impact both you, and your opponents. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^Jor's Strings are universal, after all. ","#","^int","/#","\n",{"->":".^.FeatInfoHub"},[["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-12.FeatInfoHub.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-30","flg":2},{"s":["^Tell me more about <b>Luck of the Fool</b>.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-12.FeatInfoHub.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-31","flg":2},{"s":["^Tell me more about <b>Dungeoneering Reflexes</b>.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-12.FeatInfoHub.2.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-32","flg":2},{"s":["^Tell me more about <b>Professional Cleric</b>.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-12.FeatInfoHub.3.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-33","flg":2},{"s":["^Tell me more about <b>Curved, Yet Balanced Bell</b>.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-12.FeatInfoHub.4.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-34","flg":2},{"s":["^I'm ready to make a decision. (Choose a feat.)",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-30":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-12.FeatInfoHub.c-30.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^If you're gonna gamble, might as well save yourself the biggest fails. ","#","^cha","/#","\n","^Luck of the Fool - Whenever you roll a natural 1, you get another result and take 1d4 damage. This effect can repeat to infinity. This damage cannot take you below 1 HP. ","#","^SystemText","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-13"},{"#f":5}],"c-31":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-12.FeatInfoHub.c-31.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^You've dodged enough shit to get down here. ","#","^dex","/#","\n","^In the future you'll be ready. For anything! ","#","^dex","/#","\n","^Dungeoneering Reflexes - Whenever you roll 10 or below, add an extra proficiency to the roll. ","#","^SystemText","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-13"},{"#f":5}],"c-32":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-12.FeatInfoHub.c-32.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.2.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^This is it. You feel it. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^Finally, you are... ","#","^str","/#","\n","^<b>COMPETENT</b>. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^Professional Cleric - You cannot critically fail. ","#","^SystemText","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-13"},{"#f":5}],"c-33":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-12.FeatInfoHub.c-33.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.3.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^Naturally, you should only take on challenges you are capable of succeeding at. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^This will lower any risks involved. ","#","^int","/#","\n","^Curved, Yet Balanced Bell - Whenever <i>any</i> d20 is rolled, the Strings of Jor causes the outcome to lean towards 10. The chance of critical rolls are diminished. ","#","^SystemText","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-13"},{"#f":5}],"c-34":["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-12.FeatInfoHub.c-34.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.4.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-13.decision"},{"->":".^.^.^.^.g-13"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5,"#n":"FeatInfoHub"}],{"#f":5}],"g-13":[{"->":".^.^.g-12.FeatInfoHub"},["^These are all tools of your trade. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^Each will help you in some way. Your choice here is to focus on one path. ","#","^str","/#","\n","^The gamble. The delve. The veteran. Or the thinker. ","#","^str","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-13.decision.15.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-35","flg":2},{"s":["^Pick <b>Luck of the Fool</b>.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_Witness.0.g-13.decision.16.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-36","flg":2},{"s":["^Pick <b>Dungeoneering Reflexes</b>.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Q_